    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the VANOS system has been serviced to maintain precision cam timing. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension, the turn-in remains sharp and predictable. It exhibits minor cosmetic wear typical of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, but the powertrain and chassis integrity are excellent. A true enthusiast\u2019s spec with no deferred maintenance on the major mechanical components.",
      "price": 34500.0,
